title: Software Engineer
description:
We are looking for a Software Engineer to join our team. The ideal candidate should have:
- 3+ years of experience in software development
- Strong knowledge of Python and JavaScript
- Experience with web frameworks like Django and React
- Good understanding of databases and SQL
- Excellent problem-solving skills
- Bachelor's degree in Computer Science or related field

Responsibilities:
- Develop and maintain web applications
- Write clean, maintainable, and efficient code
- Collaborate with cross-functional teams
- Participate in code reviews
- Debug and fix issues in production

Benefits:
- Competitive salary
- Flexible working hours
- Remote work options
- Health insurance
- Professional development opportunities
